fswebcam: fswebcam (Tiny and flexible webcam program)
fswebcam:
fswebcam: fswebcam is a neat and simple webcam app.  It captures images from
fswebcam: a V4L1/V4L2 compatible device or file,  averages them to reduce
fswebcam: noise and draws a caption using the GD Graphics Library which also
fswebcam: handles compressing the image to PNG or JPEG. The resulting image is
fswebcam: saved to a file or sent to stdio where it can be piped to something
fswebcam: like ncftpput or scp. 
fswebcam:
fswebcam:
